                <h1>Essential History and Physical Template for Effective Patient Care</h1>
                <p>A history and physical template is a vital tool used in healthcare to systematically document a patient's medical history and physical examination findings. It typically includes sections for personal information, past medical history, medication lists, allergies, and current symptoms. This structured format enhances efficiency and accuracy in patient assessments.</p>
